jibe.sdk.client.contacts
Class CapabilitiesUpdateEvent

java.lang.Object
  jibe.sdk.client.events.JibeEvent
      jibe.sdk.client.contacts.CapabilitiesUpdateEvent

public class CapabilitiesUpdateEvent
extends JibeEvent

The JibeEvent class for a capabilities updates. A capabilities update event always refers to a phone number (MSISDN), and may optionally also refer to a known contact.
